data.description: This stunning 4-bedroom home has undergone a complete transformation. With new granite countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms, it exudes sophistication. The fresh coat of paint and new flooring throughout breathe new life into every room. The addition of new windows brings in abundant natural light and energy efficiency. The updated master bathroom provides a serene retreat. Outside, a new pool beckons for relaxation and fun. This home is a true haven of modern living, offering both comfort and elegance.
